push all branches (this pushes new only local branches too)
-----------------
git push origin --all

get or update a file from a different branch
--------------------------------------------
git checkout mystery-pipe-opt -- FLIRanalysisPhase1aCamXPipeOpt.cpp
git add FLIRanalysisPhase1bCamXPipeOpt.cpp

status of tracked files only
---------------------------
git status -uno




